psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer

Class EntityEnricherStatisticsWriter<P extends Entity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<P>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EntityEnricherStatisticsWriter<P>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, EnricherListener<P>, EntityEnricherListener<P>, EntityChangeListener<P>, EntityInteractorChangeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ParticipantEnricherStatisticsWriter

    public class EntityEnricherStatisticsWriter<P extends Entity>
extends EnricherStatisticsWriter<P>
implements EntityEnricherListener<P>
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    18/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
